### Job Finder C# Backend — REST API Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5002
@contentType = application/json

# ─── VARIABLES (fill after login) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
@jobSeekerId = <fill after GET /jobseeker/profile>
@recruiterId = <fill after GET /recruiter/profile>
@jobId       = <fill after POST /jobs>
@applicationId = <fill after GET /jobseeker/applications>
@queueJobId  = <fill from 202 response>


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AUTH
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Signup — Job Seeker
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup/jobseeker
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test Seeker",
  "email": "seeker@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 2. Signup — Recruiter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup/recruiter
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test Recruiter",
  "email": "recruiter@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "companyName": "Acme Corp",
  "industry": "Software",
  "companyWebsite": "https://acme.com",
  "description": "A great place to work"
}

###

### 3. Login — Job Seeker
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "seeker@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 4. Login — Recruiter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "recruiter@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 5. Get Current User (requires accessToken cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

###

### 6. Refresh Tokens (requires refreshToken cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh

###

### 7. Upgrade Job Seeker to Recruiter (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/upgrade
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyName": "My New Company",
  "industry": "Tech",
  "companyWebsite": "https://mynewcompany.com",
  "description": "Startup building cool things"
}

###

### 8. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# JOBS (public + recruiter)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 9. List All Jobs (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/all

###

### 10. List Jobs — with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/all?category=Software&location=remote&search=react&page=1&pageSize=10

###

### 11. Create Job (requires RECRUITER cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Senior React Developer",
  "description": "Build amazing UIs",
  "requirements": "5+ years React, TypeScript expertise",
  "location": "Remote",
  "salaryRange": "$120,000 - $160,000",
  "category": "Software"
}

###

### 12. Get Job by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/{{jobId}}

###

### 13. Update Job (requires RECRUITER cookie)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/{{jobId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Lead React Developer",
  "description": "Build amazing UIs at scale",
  "requirements": "7+ years React, TypeScript and team lead experience",
  "location": "Remote",
  "salaryRange": "$140,000 - $180,000",
  "category": "Software"
}

###

### 14. Get My Jobs (requires RECRUITER cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/recruiter

###

### 15. Delete Job (requires RECRUITER cookie)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/{{jobId}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# JOB SEEKER
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 16. Get Job Seeker Profile (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/profile

###

### 17. Update Job Seeker Profile (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/profile
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "bio": "Passionate full-stack developer",
  "location": "Sydney, Australia",
  "skills": ["React", "TypeScript", "Node.js", "C#"],
  "education": "BSc Computer Science",
  "experience": "5 years at Acme Corp",
  "resumeUrl": "https://example.com/my-resume.pdf"
}

###

### 18. Apply to Job — enqueued (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie) → 202 Accepted
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/apply/{{jobId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "coverLetter": "I am very excited about this opportunity!"
}

###

### 19. Poll queue status for Apply job (replace queueJobId from 202 response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/queue/job/{{queueJobId}}

###

### 20. Get My Applications (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/applications

###

### 21. Withdraw Application (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/applications/{{applicationId}}

###

### 22. Save Job — enqueued (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie) → 202 Accepted
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/save/{{jobId}}

###

### 23. Get Saved Jobs (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/saved

###

### 24. Unsave Job (requires JOB_SEEKER cookie)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/saved/{{jobId}}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# RECRUITER
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 25. Get Recruiter Profile (requires RECRUITER cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recruiter/profile

###

### 26. Update Recruiter Profile (requires RECRUITER cookie)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/recruiter/profile
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "companyName": "Acme Corp Updated",
  "companyWebsite": "https://acme-updated.com",
  "description": "We build the future",
  "industry": "AI / ML"
}

###

### 27. Get Applications for a Job (requires RECRUITER cookie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recruiter/jobs/{{jobId}}/applications

###

### 28. Update Application Status (requires RECRUITER cookie)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/recruiter/applications/{{applicationId}}/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "shortlisted"
}

###

### 29. Update Application Status — rejected
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/recruiter/applications/{{applicationId}}/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "rejected"
}


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VALIDATION ERROR CASES
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 30. Signup with weak password → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup/jobseeker
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Bad User",
  "email": "bad@test.com",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### 31. Login with wrong password → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "seeker@test.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 32. Access protected endpoint without cookie → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobseeker/profile

###

### 33. Access recruiter endpoint as job seeker → 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recruiter/profile
